installationInstructions.title: broken door opener
installationInstructions.content: take six screws out of the front panel and remove the panel. remove four screws from the top handle cover that are underneath than remove it and put the buttons in the new piece . than snap the new handle cover back in place and put the four screws that hold it back in. put the front panel back on and you are done
